.TH ELEMENTARY-L10N 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "Elementary L10n Manual"
.SH NAME
elementary-l10n - Translation status viewer for elementary OS via Weblate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B elementary-l10n
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBelementary-l10n\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for viewing elementary OS translation progress via Weblate. It fetches live translation status, displays color-coded progress bars (red to yellow to green), auto-detects the system language, allows sorting by most or least translated components, and provides direct links to Weblate for contributing translations.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH KEYBOARD SHORTCUTS
.TP
.B Ctrl+Q
Quit the application
.TP
.B F5
Refresh the current data
.TP
.B Ctrl+/
Show keyboard shortcuts dialog
.TP
.B Ctrl+E
Export current view to CSV or JSON format
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/elementary-l10n/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/elementary-l10n/
Cached data.
